---
---
<section id="enterprise-pricing">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2 class="section-title">Enterprise &amp; Regulated Sectors</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">For organizations with compliance obligations: banking, energy, healthcare, public administration.</p>
    <div class="enterprise-grid">
      <div class="ent-card">
        <div class="ent-tier">Pro</div>
        <div class="ent-range">&euro;18,000 &ndash; &euro;36,000</div>
        <div class="ent-period">/year</div>
        <p>Up to 25 servers, 20 users. SIEM export, OIDC SSO. Ideal for enterprise pilot deployments.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ent-card">
        <div class="ent-tier">Business</div>
        <div class="ent-range">&euro;60,000 &ndash; &euro;120,000</div>
        <div class="ent-period">/year, per environment</div>
        <p>Up to 100 servers, unlimited users. SAML SSO, RBAC, multi-tenancy. Compliance reports included.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="ent-card">
        <div class="ent-tier">Enterprise</div>
        <div class="ent-range">&euro;150,000+</div>
        <div class="ent-period">/year, per entity</div>
        <p>Unlimited everything. HA clustering, NIS2 evidence, incident workflow. Dedicated success team.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="compliance-addon">
      <h3>Compliance-as-a-Service</h3>
      <div class="addon-range">&euro;25,000 &ndash; &euro;80,000 per audit cycle</div>
      <p>Pre-built evidence packages for EU AI Act, NIS2, DORA, SOC 2, and ISO 42001 audits. Includes gap analysis, remediation guidance, and auditor-ready documentation.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .enterprise-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(260px,1fr));
    gap:1.5rem;margin-top:2.5rem}
  .ent-card{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius:.5rem;padding:1.75rem}
  .ent-tier{font-size:.85rem;font-weight:600;color:var(--teal);
    text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.05em;margin-bottom:.5rem}
  .ent-range{font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:800;
    background:var(--grad);-webkit-background-clip:text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent}
  .ent-period{font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:1rem}
  .ent-card p{font-size:.875rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6}

  .compliance-addon{margin-top:2.5rem;background:var(--surface);
    border:1px solid var(--teal);border-radius:.5rem;padding:2rem;text-align:center}
  .compliance-addon h3{font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:.5rem}
  .addon-range{font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--teal);margin-bottom:.75rem}
  .compliance-addon p{font-size:.9rem;color:var(--muted);max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;line-height:1.6}
</style>
